Sentencas: The purpose of this study was to fabricate a porous supporting cathode for direct carbon solid oxide fuel cells (DCFC).
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of La0.65Sr0.3MnO3-δ/(Y2O3)0.08 (ZrO2)0.92/Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-δ tri-composite cathode-supported tubular direct carbon solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Therefore, the effect of Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-delta (GDC) addition on the phase stability, sintering behavior, thermal expansion, and porosity of La0.65Sr0.3MnO3-delta/(Y2O3)(0.08)(ZrO2)(0.92) (LSM/YSZ) composite was evaluated.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of La0.65Sr0.3MnO3-δ/(Y2O3)0.08 (ZrO2)0.92/Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-δ tri-composite cathode-supported tubular direct carbon solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The sintering temperature and the porosity of the LSM/YSZ composite were observed to increase with increase in the amount of GDC.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of La0.65Sr0.3MnO3-δ/(Y2O3)0.08 (ZrO2)0.92/Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-δ tri-composite cathode-supported tubular direct carbon solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: An LSM/YSZ/GDC tri-composite with optimized properties was selected to fabricate the tubular cathode-supported DCFCs (LSM/YSZ/GDCIYSZINiO/YSZ) through extrusion, slurry coating, and co-firing.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of La0.65Sr0.3MnO3-δ/(Y2O3)0.08 (ZrO2)0.92/Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-δ tri-composite cathode-supported tubular direct carbon solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: A special chamber was designed for the DCFC operation of the tubular cell.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of La0.65Sr0.3MnO3-δ/(Y2O3)0.08 (ZrO2)0.92/Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-δ tri-composite cathode-supported tubular direct carbon solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Electrochemical characterization was performed by measuring the polarization curves and electrochemical impedance spectroscopy, using the syngas produced by in situ steam gasification of carbon black.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of La0.65Sr0.3MnO3-δ/(Y2O3)0.08 (ZrO2)0.92/Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-δ tri-composite cathode-supported tubular direct carbon solid oxide fuel cell
